tip.text: Amazing atmosphere, decoration is pretty, service and hospitality is perfect. Very kind and helpful. The food is delicious! We tried the lamb from the gril, chicken and lamb in gravy. And desert try!
Love the music, great spot for family's/childeren. There is a cosy pool. Delicious food so good choice of my frienda.
I just love the view! It's so close the KL tower. Sit outside, cause inside it's too cold with the AC on and the music is so loud! Delicious cocktails, fries and other snacks.
It's incredible! Can't get enough of the view during the morning it's pretty, but during the evening it's also pretty

venue.name: Sky Deck - Swimming Pool, The Face Suite

tip.text: Great atmosphere, good Italian food, kind waiters and delicious cocktails.

As a real Indian food lover, the service is so BAD.  Keuze op 't kerstmenu maar er werd al voor je bepaald dat je alles krijgt, maar betaalt wel per persoon, belachelijk. Ik kom nooit meer hier terug!
Stunning place to grab a coffee/tea and try the cake! We had a hightea, but it was nothing special. Try the caramel cake, yummie!! 8.0
Lovely spot to chill! Beautiful view, delicious cheesecake and superduber yummie lemonades!! Definitely worth to step by.
Don't expect authentic indian food, but the food is delicious. Especially the dal you should try. The chai is a bit different, but ok. Mango lassi is good. 👌🏼 7,5!
Very kind & helpful staff. Neighborhood is not so safely,but this restaurant is decorated typically Indian style. Food ok, not very tasteful and authentic like I'm used to have. Average food 6,5
Beautiful location, fancy decorated, great and helpful staf and heavenly food! Seriously, I've not felt so good after this visit! Yummy sushi and divine desserts!
Delicious real Indian food. Lovely staff, very kind. A pretty garden so you can sit also outside. Veggie food is delicious. Only saag paneer was not so tasteful. Oh and try garam gulab jamun
Super delicious gelato! I just loved the decoration of the shop! A variety of flavors so it's difficult to choose.
Speechless view! Breathtaking. Take your photocam along and make some stunning pics
Beautiful location to have lunch/dinner and a drink. Affordable prices and tasteful food!!
The superior rooms are pretty, enough space, clean and great balkony. The breakfast is so not worth to pay€15,00. Terrible breakfast
Cosy farm to relax, enjoy the spa or Detox. Friendly staff! Ultimate present tip for a good friend or your mom
Restauranta looks pretty, dishes are served beautiful but the food and the service was disappointed! I'm Indian so I know what good Desi food is, but this was not good. Service was also bad! :(
One of my favorite spots in BCN. Enjoy the sun, sit back and relax, lovely bars and restaurants and watch people. I just love it.
The concept is great for big eaters, but I'm not so fond of it. The patata Bravas are yummie, many choices to create your own salads. Price is ok, but I expected a bit more of the food.
I'm so in love with this cosy bar/restaurant. Great ambiance, kind and funny staff, delicious tapas and cocktails! Must definitely try!
I just love Camp Nou. The best stadium and the greatest footbalclub of the world! Must do: watch a game of Barca.
Amazing shop with lots of Barca stuff such as shirts, training jackets and many more. Definitely must see during your stay at barca
Hotel is ok for a one night stand but it's not worth to upgrade your room. There is not a water cooker in the room, during your stay at your birthday there is nothing special. The breakfast is good!
